com.mindfusion.charting

Interface Series

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BarSeries, DataBoundSeries, DateTimeSeries, EventSeries, FunctionSeries, PieSeries, PointSeries, PointSeries3D, Series2D, Series3D, SimpleSeries, StockPriceSeries, XmlSeries

    public interface Series
    Specifies the interface that data providers should implement in order to feed data to SeriesRenderer classes.
